# Comments: Lower Case Only

Write all comments in **lower case** only. This applies to:

- Inline comments (`# ...`)
- Block comments

Do not capitalize the first letter of a comment or use mid-sentence capitals except for placeholders (e.g. `TODO`, `FIXME`) or other conventional tokens if the project allows them.

## Examples

```python
# ❌ BAD — capitalized
# This function fetches the user profile

# ✅ GOOD — lower case
# this function fetches the user profile
```
